@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/views

### Create a new view
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "contentId"
}

### Get all views
GET {{baseUrl}}

### Get views by content ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/content/contentId

### Get view count for content
GET {{baseUrl}}/content/contentId/count

### Get views by user ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/user/userId

### Get view by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/viewId

### Check if user has viewed content
GET {{baseUrl}}/content/contentId/check

### Delete view
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/viewId
